# Overview of USART related registers

----

= Overview of USART related registers =

Based on MPLAB version 8.83

The names in the columns are those in the MPLAB .dev files
(raw, not normalized for the Jallib device files).

When a PIC has 2 USARTs a second line is displayed.

For SPBRG registers the size is expressed in bits (betweeen brackets).
